Title: He Made a Terrible Mistake
Writer: Peter Nowalk (created by), Joe Fazzio, Erika Harrison (executive story editor), Fernanda Coppel (executive story editor), Morenike Balogun (story editor)
Actors: Viola Davis, Billy Brown, Alfred Enoch, Jack Falahee
Plot: Annalise copes with a new twist in the DA's case; alliances change in the Keating 4 as they uncover new information about Wes's death; details from the night of the fire reveal Wes's murderer.
